«Ажинияз Каракалпак» является одной из к: «Ajiniyaz Karakalpak» is one of the largest pharmacy chains in Karakalpakstan, and our goal is to provide our people with affordable and high-quality medicines.
Наша первая аптека была открыта в 2017 г: Our first pharmacy was opened in 2017 under the name «Azhiniyaz Nukus». Since 2019, we have been providing our services under the name «Ajiniyaz Karakalpak».
Название аптеки «Ажинияз Каракалпак» свя: The name of the pharmacy «Azhiniyaz Karakalpak» is associated with the historical novel of the Karakalpak poet Karamatdin Sultanov, written in 1971, called «Azhiniyaz».
Наследники поэта в 2017 году открыли сво: The poet’s heirs opened their first pharmacy in 2017 under the name «Azhiniyaz Nukus», and since 2019 they have been providing services under the name «Azhiniyaz Karakalpak».
«Ажинияз Каракалпак» аптека в Узбекистан: «Azhiniyaz Karakalpak» pharmacy in Uzbekistan became one of the first to receive a JPP certificate. This certificate confirms the compliance of our pharmacy with international standards and guarantees that the storage conditions of medicines fully comply with the requirements.
